\# self\.left \= None
\# self\.right \= None
class Solution\:
 def help\(self\, root\, result\)\:
 if not root\:
 return
 result \+\= root\.val
 self\.help\(root\.left\)
 self\.help\(root\.right\)

 def preorderTraversal\(self\, root\)\:
 """
 \:type root\: TreeNode
 \:rtype\: List\[int\]
 """
 if not root\:
 return \[\]
 result \= \[\]
 self\.help\(root\, result\)
 return result
